{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775807590460,"sessionID":"ses_289a3882bffeOqq5dMWPtOnwCy","part":{"id":"prt_d765fb22f001h7y8c12XMYIQ1D","messageID":"msg_d765f96c4001SgNiujGMLLUYrB","sessionID":"ses_289a3882bffeOqq5dMWPtOnwCy","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"call_2010f437090947e784a5e6d3","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# AR-001: CRD AgentRuntime 类型定义 — 设计说明\n\n## 1. 架构\n\n### 1.1 定位\n\n`AgentRuntime` 是 AgentCube 沙箱编排系统的核心 Custom Resource Definition (CRD)，运行于 Kubernetes API Server 中，API Group 为 `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`。它声明式地定义 AI Agent 沙箱的运行环境模板，是 WorkloadManager 控制器、client-go 生成代码、CLI/SDK 的类型基础。\n\n### 1.2 包结构\n\n```\npkg/apis/\n└── runtime/\n    └── v1alpha1/\n        ├── doc.go                  # 包文档 + k8s 代码生成标记\n        ├── groupversion_info.go    # GroupVersion + SchemeBuilder (controller-runtime 风格)\n        ├── register.go             # Kind 元数据 + Resource 辅助函数\n        ├── agent_type.go           # AgentRuntime CRD 类型定义（本变更核心）\n        ├── codeinterpreter_types.go # CodeInterpreter CRD + 共享类型 (TargetPort, ProtocolType)\n        └── zz_generated.deepcopy.go # controller-gen object 自动生成\n```\n\n### 1.3 依赖关系\n\n```\nAgentRuntime 类型定义\n  ├── k8s.io/api/core/v1          (corev1.PodSpec 嵌入)\n  ├── k8s.io/apimachinery         (metav1.TypeMeta, ObjectMeta, Duration, Condition)\n  ├── sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime (scheme.Builder)\n  │\n  ├──→ make generate              产出 zz_generated.deepcopy.go\n  ├──→ make gen-crd               产出 manifests/charts/base/crds/*.yaml\n  ├──→ make gen-client            产出 client-go/ (Typed Client, Informer, Lister)\n  └──→ WorkloadManager            通过 Informer/Lister 消费 AgentRuntime 资源\n```\n\n### 1.4 代码生成工具链\n\n| 工具 | 版本 | 用途 |\n|------|------|------|\n| controller-gen | v0.17.2 | DeepCopy 方法生成 + CRD YAML 生成 |\n| k8s.io/code-generator | v0.34.1 | client-go 代码生成 (Typed Client, Informer, Lister, Fake) |\n\n生成入口：`make gen-all` → `generate` + `gen-client`。\n\n---\n\n## 2. 数据结构\n\n### 2.1 包声明与代码生成标记 (`doc.go`)\n\n```go\n// +k8s:deepcopy-gen=package\n// +groupName=runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\npackage v1alpha1\n```\n\n- `+k8s:deepcopy-gen=package`：触发 controller-gen 为包内所有类型生成 DeepCopy 方法\n- `+groupName`：声明 API Group 名称，client-go 代码生成器读取\n\n### 2.2 GroupVersion 与 Scheme (`groupversion_info.go`)\n\n```go\npackage v1alpha1\n\nimport (\n    \"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime/schema\"\n    \"sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime/pkg/scheme\"\n)\n\nvar (\n    // GroupVersion 标识 API group 和 version\n    GroupVersion = schema.GroupVersion{Group: \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\", Version: \"v1alpha1\"}\n\n    // SchemeBuilder 用于将类型注册到 scheme\n    SchemeBuilder = &scheme.Builder{GroupVersion: GroupVersion}\n\n    // AddToScheme 将本 group 的所有类型添加到 runtime.Scheme\n    AddToScheme = SchemeBuilder.AddToScheme\n)\n```\n\n### 2.3 Kind 元数据 (`register.go`)\n\n```go\npackage v1alpha1\n\nimport \"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime/schema\"\n\nvar (\n    // CodeInterpreter Kind 元数据\n    CodeInterpreterKind             = \"CodeInterpreter\"\n    CodeInterpreterGroupKind        = GroupVersion.WithKind(\"CodeInterpreter\")\n    CodeInterpreterListKind         = \"CodeInterpreterList\"\n    CodeInterpreterGroupVersionKind = GroupVersion.WithKind(\"CodeInterpreter\")\n\n    // AgentRuntime Kind 元数据\n    AgentRuntimeKind             = \"AgentRuntime\"\n    AgentRuntimeListKind         = \"AgentRuntimeList\"\n    AgentRuntimeGroupVersionKind = GroupVersion.WithKind(\"AgentRuntime\")\n)\n\n// SchemeGroupVersion 是 GroupVersion 的别名，兼容 client-go 代码生成器\nvar SchemeGroupVersion = GroupVersion\n\n// Resource 返回指定 resource 的 GroupVersionResource\nfunc Resource(resource string) schema.GroupVersionResource {\n    return GroupVersion.WithResource(resource)\n}\n```\n\n### 2.4 共享类型 (`codeinterpreter_types.go`)\n\n以下类型被 AgentRuntime 和 CodeInterpreter 共同使用：\n\n```go\n// ProtocolType 定义端口协议\ntype ProtocolType string\n\nconst (\n    ProtocolTypeHTTP  ProtocolType = \"HTTP\"\n    ProtocolTypeHTTPS ProtocolType = \"HTTPS\"\n)\n\n// TargetPort 定义沙箱暴露的端口\ntype TargetPort struct {\n    // PathPrefix URL 路径前缀（可选）\n    PathPrefix string `json:\"pathPrefix,omitempty\"`\n    // Name 端口名称（可选）\n    Name string `json:\"name,omitempty\"`\n    // Port 端口号（必填）\n    Port uint32 `json:\"port\"`\n    // Protocol 协议类型，默认 HTTP\n    // +kubebuilder:default=HTTP\n    // +kubebuilder:validation:Enum=HTTP;HTTPS\n    Protocol ProtocolType `json:\"protocol\"`\n}\n\n// AuthModeType 定义认证模式\ntype AuthModeType string\n\nconst (\n    AuthModePicoD AuthModeType = \"picod\"\n    AuthModeNone  AuthModeType = \"none\"\n)\n```\n\n### 2.5 AgentRuntime 核心类型 (`agent_type.go`)\n\n#### 2.5.1 AgentRuntime (CR 根类型)\n\n```go\n// +genclient\n// +k8s:deepcopy-gen:interfaces=k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime.Object\n// +kubebuilder:object:root=true\n// +kubebuilder:subresource:status\n// +kubebuilder:resource:scope=Namespaced,plural=agentruntimes\n// +kubebuilder:printcolumn:name=\"Age\",type=\"date\",JSONPath=\".metadata.creationTimestamp\"\n\n// AgentRuntime 声明式定义 AI Agent 沙箱的运行环境模板。\ntype AgentRuntime struct {\n    metav1.TypeMeta   `json:\",inline\"`\n    metav1.ObjectMeta `json:\"metadata,omitempty\"`\n\n    Spec   AgentRuntimeSpec   `json:\"spec\"`\n    Status AgentRuntimeStatus `json:\"status,omitempty\"`\n}\n```\n\n**Kubebuilder 标记说明：**\n\n| 标记 | 作用 |\n|------|------|\n| `+genclient` | 为 client-go 代码生成器标识此类型需要生成 Typed Client |\n| `+k8s:deepcopy-gen:interfaces=...` | DeepCopy 方法实现 runtime.Object 接口 |\n| `+kubebuilder:object:root=true` | 标记为 kubebuilder object root，生成 DeepCopyObject |\n| `+kubebuilder:subresource:status` | 启用 `/status` 子资源，分离 spec/status 更新权限 |\n| `+kubebuilder:resource:scope=Namespaced,plural=agentruntimes` | 命名空间级资源，REST 路径复数形式为 `agentruntimes` |\n| `+kubebuilder:printcolumn:name=\"Age\"...` | `kubectl get agentruntimes` 输出中显示 Age 列 |\n\n#### 2.5.2 AgentRuntimeSpec\n\n```go\n// AgentRuntimeSpec 定义 AgentRuntime 的期望状态。\ntype AgentRuntimeSpec struct {\n    // TargetPort 沙箱暴露的端口列表\n    Ports []TargetPort `json:\"targetPort,omitempty\"`\n\n    // PodTemplate 沙箱 Pod 模板（必填）\n    // +kubebuilder:validation:Required\n    Template *SandboxTemplate `json:\"podTemplate\"`\n\n    // SessionTimeout 会话空闲超时时间，默认 15m\n    // +kubebuilder:default=\"15m\"\n    SessionTimeout *metav1.Duration `json:\"sessionTimeout,omitempty\"`\n\n    // MaxSessionDuration 会话最大存活时间，默认 8h\n    // +kubebuilder:default=\"8h\"\n    MaxSessionDuration *metav1.Duration `json:\"maxSessionDuration,omitempty\"`\n}\n```\n\n**字段语义：**\n\n| 字段 | 类型 | 必填 | 默认值 | 说明 |\n|------|------|------|--------|------|\n| `targetPort` | `[]TargetPort` | 否 | `[]` | 沙箱暴露的端口配置，为空时 WorkloadManager 不配置路由端口 |\n| `podTemplate` | `*SandboxTemplate` | 是 | — | 沙箱 Pod 模板，嵌入 `corev1.PodSpec` |\n| `sessionTimeout` | `*metav1.Duration` | 否 | `15m` | 空闲超时后沙箱被清理 |\n| `maxSessionDuration` | `*metav1.Duration` | 否 | `8h` | 沙箱从创建到强制销毁的最大时长 |\n\n#### 2.5.3 SandboxTemplate\n\n```go\n// SandboxTemplate 定义沙箱 Pod 的模板。\ntype SandboxTemplate struct {\n    // Labels 注入到沙箱 Pod 的额外标签\n    Labels map[string]string `json:\"labels,omitempty\"`\n\n    // Annotations 注入到沙箱 Pod 的额外注解\n    Annotations map[string]string `json:\"annotations,omitempty\"`\n\n    // Spec Pod 规格（必填），直接使用 Kubernetes 原生 PodSpec\n    // +kubebuilder:validation:Required\n    Spec corev1.PodSpec `json:\"spec\"`\n}\n```\n\n**设计决策：** `SandboxTemplate` 直接嵌入 `corev1.PodSpec` 而非自定义字段子集。\n\n| 方案 | 优点 | 缺点 |\n|------|------|------|\n| 嵌入 `corev1.PodSpec`（已选） | 完整 Kubernetes 能力；无需维护字段映射；与 agent-sandbox 项目一致 | CRD YAML 较大（~1000 行） |\n| 自定义字段子集 | CRD YAML 精简 | 丢失 Kubernetes 原生能力；需持续同步 PodSpec 变更 |\n\n#### 2.5.4 AgentRuntimeStatus\n\n```go\n// AgentRuntimeStatus 定义 AgentRuntime 的观测状态。\ntype AgentRuntimeStatus struct {\n    // Conditions 资源状态条件列表\n    // +optional\n    Conditions []metav1.Condition `json:\"conditions,omitempty\"`\n}\n```\n\n**预期 Condition 类型（由 WorkloadManager 控制器写入）：**\n\n| Type | Status | Reason | 说明 |\n|------|--------|--------|------|\n| `Ready` | `True` | `SandboxRunning` | 沙箱已成功创建并运行 |\n| `Ready` | `False` | `SandboxFailed` | 沙箱创建失败或异常终止 |\n| `Ready` | `Unknown` | `Pending` | 沙箱正在创建中 |\n\n#### 2.5.5 AgentRuntimeList\n\n```go\n// +k8s:deepcopy-gen:interfaces=k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime.Object\n// +kubebuilder:object:root=true\n\n// AgentRuntimeList 包含 AgentRuntime 资源列表。\ntype AgentRuntimeList struct {\n    metav1.TypeMeta `json:\",inline\"`\n    metav1.ListMeta `json:\"metadata,omitempty\"`\n    Items           []AgentRuntime `json:\"items\"`\n}\n```\n\n### 2.6 数据结构关系图\n\n```\nAgentRuntime\n├── TypeMeta (apiVersion: runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1, kind: AgentRuntime)\n├── ObjectMeta (name, namespace, labels, annotations, uid, creationTimestamp, ...)\n├── Spec: AgentRuntimeSpec\n│   ├── targetPort: []TargetPort\n│   │   ├── pathPrefix: string (optional)\n│   │   ├── name: string (optional)\n│   │   ├── port: uint32 (required)\n│   │   └── protocol: ProtocolType (default: HTTP, enum: HTTP|HTTPS)\n│   ├── podTemplate: *SandboxTemplate (required)\n│   │   ├── labels: map[string]string (optional)\n│   │   ├── annotations: map[string]string (optional)\n│   │   └── spec: corev1.PodSpec (required)\n│   │       ├── containers: []corev1.Container\n│   │       ├── volumes: []corev1.Volume\n│   │       ├── serviceAccountName: string\n│   │       ├── nodeSelector: map[string]string\n│   │       ├── tolerations: []corev1.Toleration\n│   │       └── ... (完整 Kubernetes PodSpec)\n│   ├── sessionTimeout: *metav1.Duration (default: \"15m\")\n│   └── maxSessionDuration: *metav1.Duration (default: \"8h\")\n└── Status: AgentRuntimeStatus\n    └── conditions: []metav1.Condition (optional)\n        └── {type, status, reason, message, lastTransitionTime, observedGeneration}\n```\n\n---\n\n## 3. API 契约\n\n### 3.1 GroupVersionKind (GVK)\n\n| 组件 | 值 |\n|------|-----|\n| API Group | `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh` |\n| Version | `v1alpha1` |\n| Kind | `AgentRuntime` |\n| ListKind | `AgentRuntimeList` |\n\n### 3.2 GroupVersionResource (GVR)\n\n| 组件 | 值 |\n|------|-----|\n| Group | `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh` |\n| Version | `v1alpha1` |\n| Resource | `agentruntimes` |\n| Scope | Namespaced |\n\n### 3.3 REST API 端点\n\nKubernetes API Server 自动暴露以下端点：\n\n| Method | Path | 说明 |\n|--------|------|------|\n| `POST` | `/apis/runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1/namespaces/{namespace}/agentruntimes` | 创建 AgentRuntime |\n| `GET` | `/apis/runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1/namespaces/{namespace}/agentruntimes/{name}` | 获取单个 AgentRuntime |\n| `GET` | `/apis/runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1/namespaces/{namespace}/agentruntimes` | 列出命名空间下的 AgentRuntime |\n| `GET` | `/apis/runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1/agentruntimes` | 列出所有命名空间的 AgentRuntime |\n| `PUT` | `/apis/runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1/namespaces/{namespace}/agentruntimes/{name}` | 更新 AgentRuntime (spec) |\n| `PATCH` | `/apis/runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1/namespaces/{namespace}/agentruntimes/{name}` | 补丁更新 |\n| `DELETE` | `/apis/runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1/namespaces/{namespace}/agentruntimes/{name}` | 删除 AgentRuntime |\n| `PUT` | `/apis/runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1/namespaces/{namespace}/agentruntimes/{name}/status` | 更新 status 子资源 |\n\n### 3.4 示例 YAML\n\n```yaml\napiVersion: runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1\nkind: AgentRuntime\nmetadata:\n  name: python-sandbox\n  namespace: default\nspec:\n  targetPort:\n    - name: web\n      port: 8080\n      protocol: HTTP\n      pathPrefix: /\n  podTemplate:\n    labels:\n      app: python-agent\n    annotations:\n      agentcube.io/runtime: python-3.11\n    spec:\n      containers:\n        - name: sandbox\n          image: python:3.11-slim\n          ports:\n            - containerPort: 8080\n          resources:\n            requests:\n              cpu: \"100m\"\n              memory: \"128Mi\"\n            limits:\n              cpu: \"1\"\n              memory: \"512Mi\"\n  sessionTimeout: \"15m\"\n  maxSessionDuration: \"8h\"\n```\n\n### 3.5 Scheme 注册\n\nAgentRuntime 类型通过 `SchemeBuilder` 注册到 `runtime.Scheme`：\n\n```go\nfunc init() {\n    SchemeBuilder.Register(&AgentRuntime{}, &AgentRuntimeList{})\n}\n```\n\n下游组件（WorkloadManager、client-go fake client）通过调用 `v1alpha1.AddToScheme(scheme)` 将类型注册到自身 scheme。\n\n### 3.6 生成的 client-go 接口\n\n`make gen-client` 基于本类型定义生成以下接口（详见 `deployment/client-go.md`）：\n\n| 接口 | 方法 | 说明 |\n|------|------|------|\n| `AgentRuntimeInterface` | `Create`, `Update`, `UpdateStatus`, `Delete`, `Get`, `List`, `Watch`, `Patch` | Typed REST 客户端 |\n| `AgentRuntimeInformer` | `Informer()`, `Lister()` | 共享 Informer + Lister |\n| `AgentRuntimeLister` | `List(selector)`, `AgentRuntimes(namespace)` | 只读缓存索引 |\n| `AgentRuntimeNamespaceLister` | `List(selector)`, `Get(name)` | 命名空间级只读索引 |\n\n---\n\n## 4. 错误处理\n\n### 4.1 验证错误\n\nKubernetes API Server 在资源创建/更新时自动执行 kubebuilder 标记定义的验证：\n\n| 场景 | 验证标记 | 预期错误 |\n|------|----------|----------|\n| `podTemplate` 缺失 | `+kubebuilder:validation:Required` | `422 Unprocessable Entity`: `spec.podTemplate: Required value` |\n| `podTemplate.spec` 缺失 | `+kubebuilder:validation:Required` | `422 Unprocessable Entity`: `spec.podTemplate.spec: Required value` |\n| `protocol` 非法值 | `+kubebuilder:validation:Enum=HTTP;HTTPS` | `422 Unprocessable Entity`: `spec.targetPort[*].protocol: Unsupported value` |\n| `sessionTimeout` 格式错误 | 隐式 (metav1.Duration 解析) | `422 Unprocessable Entity`: 解析失败 |\n\n### 4.2 应用层错误\n\n`pkg/api/errors.go` 定义与 AgentRuntime 相关的错误类型：\n\n```go\nvar (\n    ErrAgentRuntimeNotFound = errors.New(\"agent runtime not found\")\n    ErrTemplateMissing      = errors.New(\"resource has no pod template\")\n)\n\nfunc NewSandboxTemplateNotFoundError(namespace, name, kind string) error\n```\n\n| 错误 | 触发场景 | HTTP 状态码 |\n|------|----------|-------------|\n| `ErrAgentRuntimeNotFound` | WorkloadManager 查找不存在的 AgentRuntime | 404 |\n| `ErrTemplateMissing` | AgentRuntime 的 `podTemplate` 为 nil | 400 |\n| `NewSandboxTemplateNotFoundError` | 按 namespace/name 查找 SandboxTemplate 失败 | 404 |\n\n### 4.3 默认值处理\n\n| 字段 | 默认值 | 应用时机 |\n|------|--------|----------|\n| `sessionTimeout` | `15m` | Kubernetes API Server 在 CREATE 时通过 defaulting webhook 或 controller-gen 生成的 CRD default 注入 |\n| `maxSessionDuration` | `8h` | 同上 |\n| `targetPort[*].protocol` | `HTTP` | 同上 |\n| `targetPort` | `[]` (空切片) | Go 零值，无需注入 |\n\n### 4.4 并发安全\n\n本包定义的类型本身无状态，不涉及并发。类型实例的并发安全由使用者（Informer cache、WorkloadManager）保证：\n\n- Informer 缓存通过 `cache.SharedIndexInformer` 的 RWMutex 保证读写安全\n- DeepCopy 方法确保跨 goroutine 传递时进行值拷贝\n\n---\n\n## 5. 测试策略\n\n### 5.1 单元测试\n\n#### 5.1.1 Scheme 注册测试\n\n```go\nfunc TestSchemeRegistration(t *testing.T) {\n    scheme := runtime.NewScheme()\n    err := v1alpha1.AddToScheme(scheme)\n    assert.NoError(t, err)\n\n    // 验证 GVK 可识别\n    gvk := v1alpha1.SchemeGroupVersion.WithKind(\"AgentRuntime\")\n    obj, err := scheme.New(gvk)\n    assert.NoError(t, err)\n    assert.IsType(t, &v1alpha1.AgentRuntime{}, obj)\n\n    // 验证 List 类型\n    gvkList := v1alpha1.SchemeGroupVersion.WithKind(\"AgentRuntimeList\")\n    objList, err := scheme.New(gvkList)\n    assert.NoError(t, err)\n    assert.IsType(t, &v1alpha1.AgentRuntimeList{}, objList)\n}\n```\n\n#### 5.1.2 GVK/GVR 常量测试\n\n```go\nfunc TestGroupVersionConstants(t *testing.T) {\n    assert.Equal(t, \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\", v1alpha1.GroupVersion.Group)\n    assert.Equal(t, \"v1alpha1\", v1alpha1.GroupVersion.Version)\n    assert.Equal(t, \"AgentRuntime\", v1alpha1.AgentRuntimeKind)\n    assert.Equal(t, \"AgentRuntimeList\", v1alpha1.AgentRuntimeListKind)\n\n    gvr := v1alpha1.Resource(\"agentruntimes\")\n    assert.Equal(t, schema.GroupVersionResource{\n        Group: \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\", Version: \"v1alpha1\", Resource: \"agentruntimes\",\n    }, gvr)\n}\n```\n\n#### 5.1.3 默认值测试\n\n```go\nfunc TestAgentRuntimeDefaultValues(t *testing.T) {\n    ar := &v1alpha1.AgentRuntime{\n        Spec: v1alpha1.AgentRuntimeSpec{\n            Template: &v1alpha1.SandboxTemplate{\n                Spec: corev1.PodSpec{\n                    Containers: []corev1.Container{{Name: \"test\", Image: \"test:latest\"}},\n                },\n            },\n        },\n    }\n\n    // 验证 Go 零值行为\n    assert.Nil(t, ar.Spec.SessionTimeout)\n    assert.Nil(t, ar.Spec.MaxSessionDuration)\n    assert.Empty(t, ar.Spec.Ports)\n\n    // 验证默认值由 CRD default 注入（模拟 API Server 行为）\n    // 注意：实际默认值由 Kubernetes API Server 在 CREATE 时注入\n    // 此处仅验证类型可接受 nil 值\n}\n```\n\n#### 5.1.4 DeepCopy 生成测试\n\n```go\nfunc TestAgentRuntimeDeepCopy(t *testing.T) {\n    original := &v1alpha1.AgentRuntime{\n        ObjectMeta: metav1.ObjectMeta{Name: \"test\", Namespace: \"default\"},\n        Spec: v1alpha1.AgentRuntimeSpec{\n            Ports: []v1alpha1.TargetPort{{Name: \"web\", Port: 8080, Protocol: v1alpha1.ProtocolTypeHTTP}},\n            Template: &v1alpha1.SandboxTemplate{\n                Labels: map[string]string{\"app\": \"test\"},\n                Spec: corev1.PodSpec{\n                    Containers: []corev1.Container{{Name: \"c\", Image: \"test:latest\"}},\n                },\n            },\n            SessionTimeout:   &metav1.Duration{Duration: 30 * time.Minute},\n            MaxSessionDuration: &metav1.Duration{Duration: 4 * time.Hour},\n        },\n        Status: v1alpha1.AgentRuntimeStatus{\n            Conditions: []metav1.Condition{{\n                Type:   \"Ready\",\n                Status: metav1.ConditionTrue,\n                Reason: \"SandboxRunning\",\n            }},\n        },\n    }\n\n    copy := original.DeepCopy()\n\n    // 验证值相等\n    assert.Equal(t, original.Name, copy.Name)\n    assert.Equal(t, original.Spec.Ports[0].Port, copy.Spec.Ports[0].Port)\n\n    // 验证引用独立（修改副本不影响原件）\n    copy.Spec.Ports[0].Port = 9090\n    assert.Equal(t, uint32(8080), original.Spec.Ports[0].Port)\n\n    copy.Spec.Template.Labels[\"app\"] = \"modified\"\n    assert.Equal(t, \"test\", original.Spec.Template.Labels[\"app\"])\n}\n```\n\n#### 5.1.5 ProtocolType 枚举测试\n\n```go\nfunc TestProtocolTypeConstants(t *testing.T) {\n    assert.Equal(t, v1alpha1.ProtocolType(\"HTTP\"), v1alpha1.ProtocolTypeHTTP)\n    assert.Equal(t, v1alpha1.ProtocolType(\"HTTPS\"), v1alpha1.ProtocolTypeHTTPS)\n}\n```\n\n### 5.2 测试文件布局\n\n```\npkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/\n├── agent_type.go\n├── agent_type_test.go        # AgentRuntime 类型测试\n├── codeinterpreter_types.go\n├── codeinterpreter_types_test.go # 共享类型测试\n├── groupversion_info.go\n├── groupversion_info_test.go # Scheme 注册测试\n├── register.go\n├── register_test.go          # GVK/GVR 常量测试\n└── zz_generated.deepcopy.go\n```\n\n### 5.3 测试运行\n\n```bash\n# 运行 pkg/apis 下所有测试\ngo test ./pkg/apis/... -v\n\n# 运行带覆盖率\ngo test ./pkg/apis/... -coverprofile=coverage.out\ngo tool cover -html=coverage.out\n```\n\n### 5.4 TDD 关联\n\n本变更与 TDD 规范的关联用例：\n\n| TDD 用例 | 关联 | 说明 |\n|----------|------|------|\n| TestCase-WM-001 | 间接 | AgentRuntime 类型是 Sandbox 创建接口的输入基础 |\n| TestCase-WM-003 | 间接 | 缺失 `podTemplate` 的拦截依赖 `+kubebuilder:validation:Required` 标记 |\n\n---\n\n## 6. 实现步骤\n\n### 6.1 文件创建顺序\n\n1. `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/doc.go` — 包声明 + 生成标记\n2. `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/groupversion_info.go` — GroupVersion + SchemeBuilder\n3. `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/register.go` — Kind 元数据\n4. `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter_types.go` — 共享类型 (TargetPort, ProtocolType)\n5. `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/agent_type.go` — AgentRuntime 核心类型\n6. 运行 `make generate` — 生成 `zz_generated.deepcopy.go`\n\n### 6.2 验证检查清单\n\n- [ ] `go build ./pkg/apis/...` 编译通过\n- [ ] `make generate` 成功生成 `zz_generated.deepcopy.go`\n- [ ] `git diff --exit-code` 通过（生成文件无意外变更）\n- [ ] `AgentRuntime` GVK = `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1, Kind=AgentRuntime`\n- [ ] GVR resource = `agentruntimes`\n- [ ] `SessionTimeout` 默认值标记 = `15m`\n- [ ] `MaxSessionDuration` 默认值标记 = `8h`\n- [ ] `SandboxTemplate.Spec` 类型为 `corev1.PodSpec` 且标记为 Required\n- [ ] `+kubebuilder:subresource:status` 已添加\n- [ ] `+kubebuilder:printcolumn` Age 列已添加\n- [ ] `go test ./pkg/apis/...` 全部通过\n\n---\n\n## 7. 后续变更\n\n本变更完成后，以下变更可并行开展：\n\n| 变更 | 依赖关系 | 说明 |\n|------|----------|------|\n| AR-002 | 依赖 AR-001 | CodeInterpreter CRD 类型定义（共享 `TargetPort`、`ProtocolType`） |\n| CRD YAML 生成 | 依赖 AR-001 | `make gen-crd` 从 kubebuilder 标记产出 CRD YAML |\n| client-go 生成 | 依赖 AR-001 | `make gen-client` 产出 Typed Client/Informer/Lister |\n| WorkloadManager | 依赖 client-go 生成 | 通过 Informer/Lister 消费 AgentRuntime 资源 |\n","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-001/design.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-001/design.md","exists":true,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-001/design.md","time":{"start":1775807590442,"end":1775807590457}}}}
